## **Scope and Delimitations**

Scope of the Study

* Mobile application targeting high school students, university students, and career switchers in the Philippines during Academic Year 2026–2027

* Comprehensive profile builder capturing education history, skills (technical/soft), certifications, career interests, values, and location preferences

* Career interest assessment integrating RIASEC and Big Five frameworks with scoring across four dimensions (skill alignment, personality, values, environment)

* Dahlia AI assistant utilizing Hugging Face LLM endpoints alongside Kokoro text-to-speech and Whisper speech-to-text integrations, structurally grounded via RAG on localized Philippine career datasets

