8. Library & History (2.8): Manages saved content and user activity history through library\_saves (D15) and user\_activity\_history (D16).  
9. Path Search/Browse (2.9): Enables users to discover learning content through learning\_paths (D13) and learning\_modules (D14).  
10. Consume/Download/Save Resources (2.10): Handles resource management with storage integration and activity logging.  
11. Completion & Review (2.11): Captures learning outcomes through path\_reviews (D19) and activity tracking (D16).  
12. Select Coach Persona (2.12): Creates conversation contexts in conversations (D3) with activity logging (D16).  
13. Live Conversation (2.13): Manages voice/text interactions, writing to conversation\_messages (D4) and conversation\_attachments (D7).  
14. Live Notes (2.14): Captures user notes during conversations in conversation\_notes (D5) with activity logging (D16).  
15. End Call & Summary (2.15): Generates insights and transcripts in conversations (D3) and conversation\_transcripts (D6).  
