* End-to-End Data Journeys

The DFD highlights five critical end-to-end data journeys that demonstrate how Enroute processes user requests:

1. Onboard → Sign in: User data flows from the Onboarding process (2.1) to Account Creation (2.1), then to Email Verification (2.3), and finally to Sign-In (2.2), with continuous updates to the profiles data store (D1).  
2. Record idea → Library: Audio inputs flow through the Record Idea process (2.4), with data stored in File Storage and ideas (D8), then optionally saved to library\_saves (D15) with activity tracking (D16).  
